PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FA driver who reached speeds of more
OL,7,Fthan 100mph on the M20 in Kent, before
OL,8,Fcausing the death of two women, has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FOn the morning of 17 October 2022, it
OL,12,Fwas raining heavily which had caused
OL,13,Fstanding water on parts of the
OL,14,Fcarriageway near West Kingsdown.
OL,16,FDr Habiba Hajallie was driving to work
OL,17,Fon the coastbound side of the motorway
OL,18,Fbetween Junctions 1 and 2 when she
OL,19,Flost control of her vehicle and
OL,20,Faquaplaned.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FShe ended up on the hard shoulder with
OL,7,Fher car facing the wrong direction.
OL,9,FLisa Webber and Mark Heap were in
OL,10,Fseparate vehicles behind Dr Hajallie
OL,11,Fand both stopped to help.
OL,13,FThey were stood on the hard shoulder
OL,14,Fwhen Bilal Tahir's vehicle, a black
OL,15,FBMW X5, crashed into them.
OL,17,FDr Hajallie and Lisa Webber were
OL,18,Fdeclared dead by paramedics at the
OL,19,Fscene. Mr Heap was seriously injured
OL,20,Fand taken to hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FRoadside tests for intoxication and
OL,7,Fimpairment were carried out on the
OL,8,Fside of the motorway which Tahir
OL,9,Fpassed. He was released under
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FThe 29 year old attended a voluntary
OL,13,Finterview at Ashford Police Station in
OL,14,FNovember 2022 where he claimed he was
OL,15,Fdriving with 'due care and attention'
OL,16,Fand had not been speeding.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FHowever, officers from the Serious
OL,7,FCollision Investigation Unit found,
OL,8,Fthrough vehicle and mobile phone data,
OL,9,Fhe had continuously been speeding
OL,10,Fthroughout his journey, and had hit
OL,11,Fspeeds of more than 100mph within a
OL,12,Fmile of the incident.
OL,14,FFive seconds before the collision,
OL,15,FTahir had been travelling at 98mph
OL,16,Fwhen it is thought he lost control
OL,17,Fafter hitting standing water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
