OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FBalil Tahir, of South Gipsy Road in
OL,7,FWelling, London, was charged with two
OL,8,Fcounts of causing death by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving and one count of causing
OL,10,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,12,FHe pleaded guilty on 23 March 2026.
OL,14,FOn Friday 5 June he was sentenced at
OL,15,Fthe Old Bailey to a total of 15 years'
OL,16,Fimprisonment. He will also be
OL,17,Fdisqualified from driving for 16 years.
OL,19,FKent Police say this is the first time
OL,20,FGPS data has been used in court for a
OL,21,Fcollision case in the county.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FDetective Constable Jim Galbraith, the
OL,7,Finvestigating officer, said "The
OL,8,Fdeaths of Dr Habiba Hajallie and Lisa
OL,9,FWebber, and the significant injuries
OL,10,Fcaused to Mark Heap are a tragedy
OL,11,Fcaused by the actions of one dangerous
OL,12,Fdriver.
OL,14,FBilal Tahir was speeding recklessly
OL,15,Fthat morning in appalling weather
OL,16,Fconditions where visibility was poor
OL,17,Fand rain was pooling on the
OL,18,Fcarriageway.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FHe failed to recognise the significant
OL,7,Frisk he posed to other road users and
OL,8,Fhas devastated multiple lives as a
OL,9,Fresult.
OL,11,FHe wouldn't accept responsibility for
OL,12,Fhis actions until the weight of
OL,13,Fevidence against him led him to enter
OL,14,Fa guilty plea.
OL,16,FSpeeding risks causing death or
OL,17,Fserious injury and poor weather
OL,18,Fconditions increases this threat
OL,19,Fsignificantly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
