PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780830169
OL,3,CSpeeding driver jailed for causing the
OL,4,Cdeath of two women on motorway
OL,6,FKent Police has a zero tolerance
OL,7,Fpolicy for those who choose to break
OL,8,Fthe speed limit and our officers will
OL,9,Fcontinue to crack down on drivers who
OL,10,Fendanger other road users."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
